ferent shapes of the epigynal atrium." captionText-3="FIGURES 40–46. Menarik kecil gen. &amp; spec. nov. holotype male (40, 42, 45) and female paratype (41, 43–44, 46) from Sarawak. 40–41 Eyes, dorsal; 42–44 Claws (42, 44 right leg I, retrolateral claw, retrolateral; 43 left palp, prolateral); 45–46 Left chelicera, ventral." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911167" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911169" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911173" figureDoi-3="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911177" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6911167/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6911169/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6911173/files/figure.png" httpUri-3="https://zenodo.org/record/6911177/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Figs 17–46</figureCitation>
